title: $25 000 CIBC National Scholarship for Computer Science
from: Feb 01, 2005
to: Feb 01, 2005
org: University of Waterloo
tags: [Mathematics, Awards]
location: Waterloo, ON, Canada
---

- Awarded to applicants with outstanding scholastic standing, strong interpersonal skills, and entrepreneurial spirit
- Conditional on sustained academic performance

This provided me with an awesome opportunity to further my many passions, both technical and non-technical. It was also a much-needed exercise in writing meaningful application essays.

To CIBC, for helping to fund my education:

Thank you.
